Message.En:
Unfortunately, our livestock were attacked again 
in the middle of the night. During the day, Gort 
keeps watch, but it was probably the work of 
<LQEM>. 
Could you please eliminate <LQVA> of them 
before they come near the village?
Message.Jp:
悔しいことに、夜中にまた家畜が襲われたのです。日中はゴートさんが目を光らせてくれてるけど――
多分<LQEM>にやられたんです
<LQVA>匹、村近くに来る前に退治してくれないでしょうか
